  <brief_title>Second Line Breast Cancer Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Multi-Center Trial Comparing the Efficacy and Tolerability of 125 and 250mg of Faslodex (Long Acting ICI 182,780) With 1mg Arimidex (Anastrazole) in Postmenopausal Women With Advanced Breast Cancer.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
